        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer904669475" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer10840701284491443560">It is important to remember I read David&apos;s books as a young man, and my ratings all reflect how the books made me feel back then, 20 years ago, and not today.<br/><br/>Now, Belgarath was such a sweet book, and infused me with a sense of warmth and safety. In fact, this is probably the best way to put it:<br/><br/><img src='https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1396973188i/9212548.jpg' width='200' height='225' alt='Tiny Tim' class='gr-hostedUserImg'/><br/><br/>I&apos;m so happy!<br/>Aha! Happy go lucky me!<br/>I just go my way,<br/>Living everyday!<br/><br/>I don&apos;t worry!<br/>Worrying don&apos;t agree,<br/>Things that bother you,<br/>Never bother me!<br/><br/>Things that bother you,<br/>Never bother me<br/>I feel happy and fine!<br/>AH</span>
  <span id="freeText10840701284491443560" style="display:none">It is important to remember I read David's books as a young man, and my ratings all reflect how the books made me feel back then, 20 years ago, and not today.<br><br>Now, Belgarath was such a sweet book, and infused me with a sense of warmth and safety. In fact, this is probably the best way to put it:<br><br><img src="https://i.gr-assets.com/images/S/compressed.photo.goodreads.com/hostedimages/1396973188i/9212548.jpg" width="200" height="225" alt="Tiny Tim" class="gr-hostedUserImg"><br><br>I'm so happy!<br>Aha! Happy go lucky me!<br>I just go my way,<br>Living everyday!<br><br>I don't worry!<br>Worrying don't agree,<br>Things that bother you,<br>Never bother me!<br><br>Things that bother you,<br>Never bother me<br>I feel happy and fine!<br>AHA!<br>Living in the sunlight,<br>Loving in the moonlight<br>Having a wonderful time!<br><br>Haven't got a lot,<br>I don't need a lot<br>Coffee's only a dime<br>Living in the sunlight,<br>Loving in the moonlight,<br>Having a wonderful time!<br><br><a target="_blank" rel="noopener nofollow" href="http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c71RCAyLS1M">http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=c71RCA...</a><br><br>Imagine this while reading any one fantasy book.<br><br>Yup, there.<br>Igor</span>
