        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer73384991" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer11668259044722745713">Run out if ideas? Why not rehash the same ones you’ve already done and extend it to a book. While the first part of the book was quite good in revealing the younger Belgarath it wasn’t exactly revelatory and just a rehash of the first 10 books. And Belgarath&apos;s constant ‘pulling of whiskers’ (if I remember the term correctly) did get very annoying. That said, it was still entertaining.</span>
  <span id="freeText11668259044722745713" style="display:none">Run out if ideas? Why not rehash the same ones you’ve already done and extend it to a book. While the first part of the book was quite good in revealing the younger Belgarath it wasn’t exactly revelatory and just a rehash of the first 10 books. And Belgarath's constant ‘pulling of whiskers’ (if I remember the term correctly) did get very annoying. That said, it was still entertaining.</span>
